    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "\n(previous: #28770)\n\n- [Release guidelines](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/master/MAINTAIN.md#release-policy)\n- [Dependencies](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/master/MAINTAIN.md#third-party-dependencies)\n\n# Blocking issues\n\n- finalize`vim.pos`, `vim.range`\n    - https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/36397\n- #35149\n\n<img width=\"446\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/1359421/032fc235-ed2e-4ce4-8198-86a9c5b20d84\">\n\n\n# Pre-release (early)\n\n- [x] ~~run `scripts/download-unicode-files.sh`~~ (utf8proc 4tw)\n- [x] Bump deps in [cmake.deps/deps.txt](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/master/cmake.deps/deps.txt)\n    - [x] run `scripts/bump_deps.lua` (luajit, luv, libuv, treesitter)\n    - [x] treesitter parsers (C, Markdown, Lua, Query, Vim, Vimdoc)\n        - [x] update queries from nvim-treesitter\n    - [x] lpeg, libiconv, gettext ([neovim/deps/opt](https://github.com/neovim/deps/tree/master/opt))\n    - [x] libvterm\n    - [x] mpack\n    - [x] ~~[wintools](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/9319d97679053a219b1701d70abce414d0f6a8b0/cmake.deps/deps.txt#L28-L36)~~\n- [x] check s930x CI logs for errors pertaining to big-endian systems \n\n# Pre-release\n\n- [x] Clean up `news.txt` (sorting, [phrasing](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qs8Gohi1e04))\n- [x] Merge `nvim.appdata.xml` changes from the maintenance branch\n- [x] Run `scripts/release.sh`\n\n# Post-release\n\n- [ ] Push `v0.12.0` tag to https://github.com/neovim/neovim-releases/tags and run the release workflow\n- [x] For major releases, create a new `release-x.y` branch.\n    - **Bump the version in CMakeLists.txt** and set `NVIM_VERSION_PRERELEASE`.\n- [x] Move `news.txt` to `news-x.y.txt`. Recreate `news.txt` with \"skeleton\" from the old one.\n- [ ] Review [revisit-at-release issues](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/labels/revisit-at-release)\n- [ ] Newsletter https://github.com/neovim/neovim.github.io\n- [ ] Update [GitHub Sponsors page](https://github.com/sponsors/neovim) (what was done, what is planned)\n- [x] Update [roadmap](https://neovim.io/roadmap/)\n- [ ] Remove deprecated functions marked for removal (`vim.deprecate(…, '0.12')`)\n- [ ] Remove deprecated:\n    - N/A\n\n# Merge these after release\n\n- [revisit-at-release PRs](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/labels/revisit-at-release)\n\n",
